--------------------------------------------------
Obsidian Items Mod
Copyright (C) Michael Joyce 2011
--------------------------------------------------

Obsidian Items Mod adds various obsidian craftables to Minecraft. Check below for a full recipe list.


--------------------------------------------------
Recipes
--------------------------------------------------

For the following recipes:
    O = Obsidian Bar
    D = Diamond
    . = Blank

Obsidian Bar
    Smelt a block of Obsidian. One block of obsidian gives one obsidian bar

Obsidian Pick
    OOO
    .D.
    .D.

Obsidian Axe
    OO.
    OD.
    .D.

Obsidian Hoe 
    OO.
    .D.
    .D.

Obsidian Spade 
    .O.
    .D.
    .D.

Obsidian Sword 
    .O.
    .O.
    .D.

